lightning
------------------------------------------
GNU lightning is a library to aid in making portable programs
that compiles assembly code at run time.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  liblightning-devel-2.1.2-1bl1
  liblightning1-2.1.2-1bl1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.28-3
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-5
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.gnu.org/software/lightning/

Canonical download:
  mirror://gnu/lightning/lightning-2.1.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lightning-2.1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lightning-2.1.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lightning-2.1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lightning-2.1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightning1-2.1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightning-devel-2.1.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lightning)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lightning.README
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/README
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/THANKS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/TODO

(liblightning1)
  /usr/bin/cyglightning-1.dll

(liblightning-devel)
  /usr/include/lightning.h
  /usr/include/lightning/jit_x86.h
  /usr/lib/liblightning.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/lightning.pc
  /usr/share/info/lightning.info.gz

